    <h1>Contact CalcPhi</h1>
    <p>We are a small, focused team and we read every message we receive. Whether you have spotted a calculation error, have a suggestion, or are interested in working with us — reach out and we will get back to you.</p>

    <h2>General Support & Feedback</h2>
    <p>For all general questions, feedback, and calculator-related queries:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@blackbeltcodelabs.com">support@blackbeltcodelabs.com</a></p>
    <p>We aim to respond within <strong>2 business days</strong> (Monday–Friday, IST). For faster answers to common questions, check our <a href="/help/">Help section</a> first.</p>

    <h2>Report a Calculation Error</h2>
    <p>Accuracy is the most important thing we do. If you believe a calculator is producing an incorrect result, please let us know. When reporting an error, it helps to include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The name of the calculator (e.g. SIP Calculator)</li>
      <li>The exact inputs you used</li>
      <li>The result CalcPhi showed you</li>
      <li>The result you expected, with a source or reference if you have one</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Send error reports to: <a href="mailto:support@blackbeltcodelabs.com">support@blackbeltcodelabs.com</a> with the subject line <strong>"Calculation Error — [Calculator Name]"</strong>.</p>
    <p>Verified errors are corrected within 48 hours and the correction is noted on the relevant page.</p>

    <h2>Advertising & Partnerships</h2>
    <p>CalcPhi reaches high-intent finance audiences at the moment they are actively evaluating financial products. We work with financial brands through display advertising and contextual affiliate partnerships.</p>
    <p>If you represent a financial product or service relevant to our audience — mutual fund platforms, loan providers, insurance companies, tax software — we would be happy to discuss how we can work together.</p>
    <p>Partnership enquiries: <a href="mailto:support@blackbeltcodelabs.com">support@blackbeltcodelabs.com</a> with the subject line <strong>"Partnership Enquiry"</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Content & Editorial</h2>
    <p>If you are a financial professional, researcher, or SEBI/SEC-registered advisor who would like to contribute to or review CalcPhi content, we welcome that conversation.</p>
    <p>Send editorial enquiries to: <a href="mailto:support@blackbeltcodelabs.com">support@blackbeltcodelabs.com</a> with the subject line <strong>"Editorial"</strong>.</p>

    <h2>About the Company</h2>
    <p>CalcPhi is developed and maintained by <strong>Black Belt Code Labs</strong>. For more information about us, visit our <a href="/about/">About page</a>.</p>

